{"tid":1462790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「呻文」你地塞得岩你地無做錯到","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:29.000Z","uid":64810,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3ed2c61e825cdc112323a1e4b7f2d53cb9c0b5","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"人地condom仔自己人都唔會割自己人 而連登足不出戶既冷氣軍師就瘋狂開post屌人 真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n我係支持用人海戰術間接方式塞機場<br />\n好唔，今日塞到班旅客 我想講咁依家唔做都做左啦 成班事後孔明咁既軍師就瘋狂屌人 （又唔考慮下現場既259既滲透程度 ）而唔係做一d貢獻/建議下一步點做/彌補<br />\n<br />\n我琴日去過機場接機又上過前線 我每分鐘都要做決定 加上資訊量極少 做錯決定有咩出奇 你咁撚叻未落機場去同人討論/舉手投票囉又唔係唔比你參加<br />\n前線做撚完左野之後 出返市區就見到成版post屌尻我地 完全無實質既建議/意見比前線<br />\n你地班人真係好撚不負責任<br />\n<br />\nBtw 琴日同今日機場既手足都做得好 你地無做錯到 而我都唔會繼續嬲9冷氣軍師 因為根本唔知班軍師係咪condom仔/三毛既分化 post<br />\n呻完"},{"pid":"9e085f4fca34c730578b9ab33972e7e362f24d83","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb44f60e1a0f0fef5111882742ebbea5c748ca7","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6656bedfd759743bda130bc7b5cf2cc94ca3acc1","tid":1462790,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d67495af3f9e366438cb0f1c02f293e68a18515","tid":1462790,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n****<br />\n今日有不足，都係因為我地冇綱領，冇方針係我地少人要點，呢個係我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集體問題</span></span></strong>，說好的塞爆結果冇人。<br />\n<br />\n解決問題係一齊解決。<br />\n唔係搵人出黎鬧。<br />\n<br />\n冇入黎就等於你冇contribute過。<br />\n指手劃腳不如你親自現場提出！<br />\n<br />\n依家就入黎，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好委屈左手足兄弟！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n班藍絲核爆都唔割，我地跌個銀仔就大呼小叫，係咪傻撚左？"},{"pid":"2506362bccfc38aad1c5fde185c8a3a8726cf9af","tid":1462790,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acfcf967638f4d35df495fe3ce99208f72ee59a","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6b6ae1e863a326f795ba34091b27a1302df543","tid":1462790,"uid":285517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2b9c08ce5813074e47b601ee20ab1b63959985","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302f3bb1ed7eeaa3738211f446db8cb1f13c3ace","tid":1462790,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d383225ffedd90e5ec1d666e6762962118c32a11","tid":1462790,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"無錯 叫到成班人屌人塞遊客真係幾灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為機場網絡差到用wifi同data都唔會穩定 出到post都基本係冷氣軍師 <br />\n重點係昨晚又唔討論做咩 係都要做緊先黎話呢樣唔好 個樣唔好 屌完又唔講多d意見<br />\n咁聽日有其他情況又點啦 不如出黎同現場討論好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoj